node.text: Check out this clip from our EXCLUSIVE interview with former VP of Afghanistan and current Afghan opposition leader Amrullah Saleh.

node.accessibility_caption: Photo shared by Sean Hannity on August 27, 2021 tagging @lindseygrahamsc, and @repmichaelwaltz. May be an image of 2 people and text that says 'GOP LAWMAKERS CALL ON BIDEN TO RECOGNIZE AFGHAN OPPOSITON FORCES TUNE INTO Hannity TONIGHT 9PM ET'.

node.text: Rep. Michael Waltz and Sen. Lindsey Graham are calling on the Biden administration to recognize Afghan opposition forces in the Panjshir Valley. The lawmakers are also asking the Biden administration “to recognize that the Afghan Constitution is still intact, and the Afghan Taliban takeover is illegal.” Sen. Graham and Rep. Waltz will react to our EXCLUSIVE interview with Afghan opposition leader Amrullah Saleh TONIGHT on “Hannity.”

node.text: President Biden used Israeli Prime Minister Naftali Bennett as an excuse to not take reporters’ questions on Afghanistan! After yesterday’s bizarre Q&A it’s easy to see why Biden would want to avoid questions about the disaster his administration created. We’ll discuss the situation in Afghanistan and bring you experts’ reactions TONIGHT on “Hannity.”

node.accessibility_caption: Photo by Sean Hannity on August 27, 2021. May be an image of 1 person, sitting and text that says 'Hannity EXCLUSIVE INTERVIEW AFGHAN OPPOSITION LEADER AMRULLAH SALEH Photo edit: PPh oto/Musadeq Sadeq'.

node.text: HANNITY EXCLUSIVE: Afghan opposition leader and former VP of Afghanistan Amrullah Saleh will join “Hannity” TONIGHT to discuss the Taliban’s takeover and the opposition forces in the Panjshir Valley. Tune in at 9 PM ET or set your DVR for this EXCLUSIVE interview!
